      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? You are going to love this car! It's been such a fantastic vehicle for me, and I've made sure to keep it well-maintained and running smoothly. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and is just waiting for someone new to take it on some adventures. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this beauty will get you there with a smile. I'm happy to answer any questions you have\u2014come check it out!",
