    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including VANOS timing adjustment and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural integrity. The suspension retains its tactile feedback with updated bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the atmospheric induction note remains crisp through the 8,000 RPM redline. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car with excellent throttle response and chassis composure.",
